Condor's hiding place, is suddenly ripped apart, as the two headed dragon
Sinnertwin catches up to his prey. "This Autobot first" one head yells, as
he lowers his mouth towards Condor, "Yes then the rest, DIE" says the
other, as they both emmit fire from their mouths at condor. The cannon on
his back follows with them, and emmits flame as well.
